{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-006__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-006", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.1", "text_original": "思齊大任，文王之母，思媚周姜。京室之婦，大姒嗣徽音，則百斯男。", "text_normalized": "思齊大任，文王之母，思媚周姜。京室之婦，大姒嗣徽音，則百斯男。", "notes": "思齊 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-006", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.2", "text_original": "惠于宗公，神罔時怨，神罔時恫。刑于寡妻，至于兄弟，以御于家邦。", "text_normalized": "惠于宗公，神罔時怨，神罔時恫。刑于寡妻，至于兄弟，以御于家邦。", "notes": "思齊 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-006__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-006", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.3", "text_original": "雝雝在宮，肅肅在廟。不顯亦臨，無射亦保。", "text_normalized": "雝雝在宮，肅肅在廟。不顯亦臨，無射亦保。", "notes": "思齊 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-006__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-006", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.4", "text_original": "肆戎疾不殄，烈假不瑕。不聞亦式，不諫亦入。", "text_normalized": "肆戎疾不殄，烈假不瑕。不聞亦式，不諫亦入。", "notes": "思齊 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-006__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-006", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.5", "text_original": "肆成人有德，小子有造。古之人無斁，譽髦斯士。", "text_normalized": "肆成人有德，小子有造。古之人無斁，譽髦斯士。", "notes": "思齊 Chinese stanza 5."}
